WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.446 --> 00:00:15.101
What will you cook for us?

00:00:22.223 --> 00:00:27.067
Ingredients required to make Beetroot-Dates &amp; Semolina Rolls

00:00:27.983 --> 00:00:32.568
Grated Beetroot, Ground Dates, Semolina, Cashews,

00:00:33.135 --> 00:00:37.203
Cherries, Cardamom Powder, Honey &amp; Ghee

00:00:37.955 --> 00:00:46.831
Take a pan and heat 2 tbsp of ghee on medium flame

00:01:02.962 --> 00:01:07.073
Add the grated beetroot into the pan, a bowlful

00:01:19.146 --> 00:01:21.645
Take it in a bowl after frying

00:01:26.096 --> 00:01:30.545
Add some more ghee in the pan

00:01:44.125 --> 00:01:50.027
Add a bowl of semolina with a spoon of sugar into the pan

00:02:07.084 --> 00:02:10.716
After frying it, take it in a bowl along with the beetroot

00:02:15.784 --> 00:02:21.784
Grind the seedless dates into a paste

00:02:35.925 --> 00:02:45.699
Mix the ground dates with the beetroot and semolina

00:02:53.527 --> 00:02:57.565
Add a little honey to the mixture

00:03:02.091 --> 00:03:08.509
Add some ghee fried cashews

00:03:10.547 --> 00:03:13.762
Also, add some cardamom powder

00:03:17.041 --> 00:03:24.834
Mix it well and roll it into small balls

00:03:35.511 --> 00:03:37.573
And the rolls are ready to serve

